claim.claim-text:
5. Key according to one or more of claims 1-4, where the flat key (30) can be pivoted between its home position and its working position (30.2; 30.1) in the container (10); 
where the push button (40) serves as a pivot bearing (33) for the flat key (30), and where its spring-loading (41) tries to pivot the flat key (30) outward (49) into its working position (30.1); characterized in that 
the insertion direction (55) of the electrocapsule (50) into the key container (10) is on a plane which is parallel to the plane of the pivoting motion (29) of the flat key (30).
